## 契约锁(Qiyuesuo) SRC专有模式

### 目标范围
- *.qiyuesuo.com (公有云)
- *.qiyuesuo.me (私有化环境1)
- *.qiyuesuo.cn (私有化环境2)

### 核心技术栈
- 前端: Nuxt.js (Vue 2 SSR) + Element UI
- 后端: Spring Boot + Express
- 认证: CAS SSO (passport子域)
- WAF: 华为云WAF (HWWAFSESID cookie)
- CAPTCHA: Geetest极验滑块
- CDN/OSS: 华为云OBS (openresty)

### 已确认高价值端点
```
passport.*/health → 内网IP泄露(无需认证)
auth.*/health → 内网IP泄露(无需认证)
open.qiyuesuo.com/api/doc/info → 完整API文档树(无需认证)
open.qiyuesuo.com/api/sdklist?type=java → SDK版本列表
cdn.qiyuesuo.com/_nuxt/*.js → 可能泄露pocToken/内部域名
dl.qiyuesuo.com/sdk/java/sdk-java-*.zip → SDK下载(含120+ API端点)
```

### CORS配置缺陷(全系)
所有passport/auth子域反射任意Origin + Credentials:true:
```bash
for d in passport.qiyuesuo.com passport.qiyuesuo.me passport.qiyuesuo.cn app37.qiyuesuo.cn; do
    curl -sk -D- "https://$d/" -H "Origin: https://evil.com" --max-time 6 | grep access-control-allow
done
```

### SDK逆向提取API端点
```bash
curl -sk "https://dl.qiyuesuo.com/sdk/java/sdk-java-4.0.0.zip" -o /tmp/sdk.zip
cd /tmp && unzip sdk.zip -d sdk && cd sdk
# 解压JAR并反编译
jar xf *.jar && find . -name "*.class" | while read f; do cfr "$f" 2>/dev/null; done
# 搜索API路径
grep -rP '"/v[23]/[a-zA-Z]+' *.java | sort -u
```

详细技术记录见 `references/qiyuesuo-src-patterns.md`

